This paper deals with list decoding of polar codes, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). It also involves the use of data structures and algorithms (cs.CC), as well as the analysis of time and space complexity (cs.DS). The authors also mention the use of polar codes in wireless communication systems (cs.NI) and the consideration of processes with memory (cs.SI).
